# CI & deploy

## GitHub Actions

- Changes should keep jobs green: Ruby setup with `bundler-cache`, Postgres service for tests, env vars matching `.github/workflows/ci.yml` (e.g. `DATABASE_URL`).
- Security steps mirror local scripts: `bin/brakeman`, `bin/bundler-audit`, `bin/importmap audit`, `bin/rubocop`.

## Kamal

- `config/deploy.yml` defines deploy targets and accessories; editing deploy config should stay in sync with how the app is run in production (env secrets, DB, Thruster/Puma, etc.).
